 270 INK 1: PLOT 112,72: DRAW 0,-40: PLOT 113,72: DRAW 0,-40
 280 INK 4: PLOT 144,72: DRAW 0,-40: PLOT 145,72: DRAW 0,-40
 290 INK 6: PLOT 176,72: DRAW 0,-40: PLOT 177,72: DRAW 0,-40
