 310 PRINT AT 19,8; INK 2; BRIGHT 1;"1"
 320 PRINT AT 19,12; INK 1; BRIGHT 1;"2"
 330 PRINT AT 19,16; INK 4; BRIGHT 1;"3"
 340 PRINT AT 19,20; INK 6; BRIGHT 1;"4"
 350 REM === Title and prompt ===
 360 LET r=0: LET t$="WIRE PANIC": INK 2: BRIGHT 1: GO SUB 3000: BRIGHT 0
 370 LET r=21: LET t$="Cut a wire: 1 2 3 4": INK 5: GO SUB 3000
 380 REM === Timer bar outline ===
